snippet.textDisplay: It took awhile for this pandemic to spread inside of mainland China, and has now been exported around the world via air travel. By the middle of February we will see multiple outbreaks all over the world, and it could possibly be terrible for third world countries. If it is truly a bio weapon gone wrong expirement the implications could be grave. People that have this virus could travel long distances before becoming sick, and in the process spread it to others while not knowing, causing this to spread exponentially. If this Corona Virus was an accident/intentional, we can expect to see multiple outbreaks all over the world given our air travel today. If this is a Zoontic disease you could expect the animals that transmit this to have a high mortality rate in the area they live or are "kept". If not, then this would mean man has had some nefarious dealings in the spread of such a virus. Surveillance is key if the disease agent was spread intentionally. The reason being is that the use of cameras, drones etc can help detect those infected and the rate an area at which the virus is spreading. Unfortunately in this current event know one will probably ever know if this was intentional due to the fact that this originated in China. The Chinese government will keep this tight lipped and under wraps as best they can to save themselves some embarrassment. The fact that it can take up to 21 days before a person to show symptoms, and add to that, that you can spread this virus without showing symptoms is problematic itself. Problematic in that health care professionals can catch it, and not know it, and that can seriously affect a nation's care for its citizens, if its nurses and doctors are stricken with this virus. There are those that do not believe this to be a true actual tragedy that is unfolding. I for one am not convinced of this, for as much as I exercise common sense and logic, and am not prone to believing in our media or government the majority of the time when stories break. If one does some simple research, and thinks for themselves, you can put two and two together and get the right answer on what is really going on. For this to be a well orchestrated event between nations, and their perspective propaganda networks would be a huge undertaking, and as much as I want to believe that would be the case, research, prayer, and commonsense tell me otherwise. There are evil people, and governments in the world with nefarious plans for humanity. In conclusion, and more will be written, we must always be ready to protect ourselves, "think" for ourselves, and not buy into the propaganda from the majority, and in my case trust in Christ alone for my eternal salvation for that is the greatest tragedy for a human soul is to perish in eternal anguish and pain of hell. I'm prepped and will keep prepping, and continue to put this before The Lord Jesus to those who are being infected and affected by this supposed Novel Corona Virus.
